         <abstract>
            <p>This paper describes the background and development of a new, low cost and more effective system for controlling the vehicle roll on leaf spring suspended vehicles. The new anti-roll concept is most effective and efficient when applied to the higher technology, parabolic tapered, leaf springs. The highest gains are available when these are used on medium and heavy duty trucks and buses.</p>
